overview: Tori is getting cold feet and having second thoughts about her upcoming wedding - especially when her boyfriend constantly hits on Annie! Well, two can play the cheating game, which Tori proves when she calls a friend over for a shoulder to weep on. Also, Monica loves to remind her that life can be just as sweet for a single gal. Don't miss Adam & Eve's look at fidelity and finality!
title: Naked Hollywood 11: Wedding Bell Blues
